column5: Two years in a row with Loon Haunt. I darn near feel overly-blessed. Now I just have to wrangle travel.... flights into INL are not looking great. Might have to drive from MSP. Ugh.

Looking at my trip to God's River / departure Winnipeg for next year. My best routing is ABQ to Minneapolis to Winnipeg. Looking like around 600. Then you are about a 5-6 hour drive to Red Lake. For years this is how I got to Red Lake. If you want to splurge and take the rental car out of the equation there is a commuter jet service Peg to Red Lake. Brett
